      public int setReservation(String country, int day, int month, int year)
      Sets a reservation for an inputted date, checks if user has money and if there are not a lot of people reserved for one date
      Parameters:
      country - string of country to decide, which fee should be used
      day - day in a date
      month - month in a date
      year - year in a date
      Returns:
      result of reservation: 0 - reservation was set, 1 - Not enough fund, 2 - Already reserved, 3 - Too many people reserved
